room_title: Escape room "Time Machine" by Get Out Escape Room in Tyler
room_description: The date is November 22, 1963, and you have a chance to warn President John F. Kennedy and his wife not to go through downtown Dallas where Lee Harvey Oswald awaits. Think you can solve the ten clues in this room and activate the Time Machine? Think you can save JFK? Think you can change history? Think you can Get Out?
